I(A) =\int d\theta_1d\theta_2~ \exp\Bigg[\frac{1}{2}(\theta,A\theta)\Bigg]=\int d\theta_1d\theta_2~ (1+\theta_1\theta_2A_{12}) = A_{12}=\sqrt{\det A}
