A:=\begin{bmatrix} 0    & 1       & \;     & \;    \\ \;-1    & 0     &  & \;    \\      \;     & \;      & 0 & 1     \\ \;     & \;      & -1 & 0     \\ \;     & \;      & \;     & \, &\ddots   \\ \end{bmatrix}.
I(A) = \int d\theta_n\dots d\theta_1\,\exp\Bigg[\frac{1}{2}(\theta,A\theta)\Bigg]\\ =  \int d\theta_n\dots d\theta_1\, (\theta_1\theta_2+\theta_3\theta_4+\cdots)\\=0
I(A) = 1.
\int d\theta_n\dots d\theta_1\, \theta_n\dots \theta_1\, = 1 
